# Screen Friend / 화면 친구 — environment template
#
# Copy to .env.local (never .env) and fill in real values.
# .env and .env.* are gitignored — DO NOT commit real keys.
#
# ⚠️  Vite exposes VITE_* variables to the renderer (browser-visible).
#     Never put secret API keys in VITE_* variables.
#     API keys must go in the Electron main process only (IPC bridge).
#
# MVP (Slices 0–8.5) needs no secrets.
# The variables below are only needed from Slice 9F onwards.

# Recraft AI image generation (Slice 9F+)
# ⚠️  A PAID Recraft account is required — free tier must not be used for real generation.
#
# Free-tier restrictions (verified 2026-06-13, official):
#   - Commercial use: NOT permitted
#   - Generated images: PUBLIC in the Recraft community gallery
#   - Output ownership: belongs to Recraft, not the user
#
# Using a free-tier key would publish user-derived characters publicly and forfeit
# ownership — a hard legal and privacy stop, not a technical limitation.
#
# Confirm your account is on a paid plan before adding a key here.
# See docs/9f-entry-decision.md §5a for enforcement details.
RECRAFT_API_KEY=your_recraft_key_here
